---
title: Easy Garlicky Herb Chicken with Romesco Roast Potatoes & Sautéed Veggies
description: When you think vibrant romesco sauce does it conjure the taste of a mouth-watering sauce over a tender slice of meat or in a pasta? If it does, we’re here to paint a new tasty picture, try drizzling it over roasted potato chunks and don’t worry, the herbs and garlic will do the trick to make this chicken enticing.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
